# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and on checkout, regardless of the
# local core.autocrlf setting. Without this, a Windows checkout with core.autocrlf=true
# converts LF blobs to CRLF locally, which then makes every one of those files show up
# as "modified" in git status/diff even though nothing was actually edited.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Known binary types: never attempt line-ending normalization or text diffing on these.
*.gif binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
